      "content": "Powerhouse has developed a library of open-source legal templates to simplify the setup and operation of SNO entities. These templates include Contributor Agreements, MPAs, and licensing contracts, reducing the complexity and cost of navigating legal requirements. By standardizing these processes, Powerhouse enables SNOs to focus on innovation and growth rather than legal overhead.",
